B=T\times N
N'=(B\times T)'=B'\times T+ B\times T'=-\tau N\times T +\kappa B\times N=-\tau(-B)+\kappa (-T)=-\kappa T+\tau B
B, T, N
B\cdot N = 0 = T \cdot N
 0 = \frac{d}{ds} (B\cdot N) = \dot{B} \cdot N + B \cdot \dot{N} 
\dot{B}
T\cdot N
N\cdot\dot{N} = \frac12 \frac{d}{ds} (N\cdot N) = 0
 \dot{N} = (\dot{N}\cdot N) N + (\dot{N}\cdot B) B + (\dot{N}\cdot T) T = 0N - (\dot{B}\cdot N) B - (\dot{T}\cdot N) T 
